## Pre-Commit Checklist

Before marking ANY feature complete:

1. ✅ Run all tests: `pytest` (backend) and `npm test` (frontend)
2. ✅ Test manually in browser
3. ✅ Check for code duplication: `grep -r "duplicate_pattern" .`
4. ✅ Verify E2E flow works
5. ✅ Code is simple and readable
6. ✅ No debug code (console.log, print statements)
7. ✅ Documentation updated

