## Quick Reference

| Issue Type | Solution Approach |
|------------|------------------|
| Bug fix | Minimal targeted change + test |
| New feature | Backend → Frontend → E2E test |
| Refactor | Extract common patterns only |
| Performance | Profile first, optimize specific bottleneck |
| Code smell | Simplify, don't add complexity |
